  cat <<'USAGE'
Usage:
  ./tools/fw host-image
  ./tools/fw docs-image
  ./tools/fw sdk-image

  ./tools/fw host-test
  ./tools/fw routegen
  ./tools/fw docgen
  ./tools/fw docs
  ./tools/fw clean

  ./tools/fw shell-host
  ./tools/fw shell-docs
  ./tools/fw shell-sdk

  ./tools/fw sdk-ports
  ./tools/fw sdk-port-resolve

  ./tools/fw sdk-check
  ./tools/fw sdk-defconfig
  ./tools/fw sdk-menuconfig
  ./tools/fw sdk-build
  ./tools/fw sdk-clean-target
  ./tools/fw sdk-distclean
  ./tools/fw sdk-flash
  ./tools/fw sdk-flash-manual
  ./tools/fw sdk-monitor
  ./tools/fw sdk-simple-monitor

  ./tools/fw hil-i2c-build
  ./tools/fw hil-i2c-flash
  ./tools/fw hil-i2c-monitor
  ./tools/fw hil-i2c-run

  ./tools/fw hil-onewire-build
  ./tools/fw hil-onewire-flash
  ./tools/fw hil-onewire-monitor
  ./tools/fw hil-onewire-run

Notes:
  - All developer-facing validation runs inside Docker by default.
  - Containers write back to the bind mount using the caller UID:GID.
  - Set DOCKER_BIN, FW_HOST_IMAGE, FW_DOCS_IMAGE, FW_SDK_IMAGE, FW_RUN_USER,
    FW_SDK_PROJECT_DIR, FW_ESPPORT, FW_MONITOR_BAUD, FW_FLASH_BEFORE,
    FW_FLASH_AFTER, FW_FLASH_RETRIES, or FW_FLASH_RETRY_DELAY_S to override defaults.
